{
  "work_slug": "alices-adventures-in-wonderland-by-lewis-carroll-5",
  "work_title": "Alice's Adventures in Wonderland (version 4)",
  "work_author": "Lewis Carroll",
  "audio_file": "audio-09",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/alices_adventures_1005_librivox/wonderland_09_carroll.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "09 - The Mock Turtle's Story",
  "reader_name": "Eric Leach",
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.768,
  "page_num": 2,
  "page_total": 4,
  "page_start_sec": 255.56,
  "page_end_sec": 496.4,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 255.56,
      "end": 258.52,
      "text": "I make you a present of everything I've said as yet."
    },
    {
      "start": 259.42,
      "end": 261.16,
      "text": "A cheap sort of present! thought Alice.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 261.86,
      "end": 264.1,
      "text": "I'm glad they don't give birthday presents like that!"
    },
    {
      "start": 264.56,
      "end": 266.34,
      "text": "But she did not venture to say it out loud."
    },
    {
      "start": 267.744,
      "end": 270.0,
      "text": "Thinking again? the Duchess asked, with",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 270.0,
      "end": 271.76,
      "text": "another dig of her sharp little chin."
    },
    {
      "start": 273.06,
      "end": 273.88,
      "text": "I've a right to think,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 274.04,
      "end": 275.02,
      "text": "said Alice sharply,"
    },
    {
      "start": 275.2,
      "end": 277.04,
      "text": "for she was beginning to feel a little worried."
    },
    {
      "start": 278.0,
      "end": 279.28,
      "text": "Just about as much right,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 279.46,
      "end": 280.48,
      "text": "said the Duchess,"
    },
    {
      "start": 280.5,
      "end": 281.74,
      "text": "as pigs have to fly;"
    },
    {
      "start": 281.98,
      "end": 282.84,
      "text": "and the m----"
    },
    {
      "start": 283.52,
      "end": 283.84,
      "text": "But here,"
    },
    {
      "start": 283.98,
      "end": 285.2,
      "text": "to Alice's great surprise,"
    },
    {
      "start": 285.52,
      "end": 287.02,
      "text": "the Duchess's voice died away,"
    },
    {
      "start": 287.22,
      "end": 289.0,
      "text": "even in the middle of her favourite word,"
    },
    {
      "start": 289.2,
      "end": 289.54,
      "text": "moral,"
    },
    {
      "start": 290.14,
      "end": 292.86,
      "text": "and the arm that was linked into hers began to tremble."
    },
    {
      "start": 293.504,
      "end": 294.2,
      "text": "Alice looked up,"
    },
    {
      "start": 294.24,
      "end": 295.9,
      "text": "and there stood the Queen in front of them,"
    },
    {
      "start": 295.98,
      "end": 296.96,
      "text": "with her arms folded,"
    },
    {
      "start": 297.14,
      "end": 298.22,
      "text": "frowning like a thunderstorm."
    },
    {
      "start": 299.66,
      "end": 300.52,
      "text": "A fine day,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 300.74,
      "end": 301.34,
      "text": "your Majesty!"
    },
    {
      "start": 302.14,
      "end": 304.42,
      "text": "the Duchess began in a low, weak voice."
    },
    {
      "start": 305.8,
      "end": 309.42,
      "text": "Now, I give you fair warning, shouted the Queen, stamping on",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 309.42,
      "end": 310.44,
      "text": "the ground as she spoke;"
    },
    {
      "start": 311.5,
      "end": 313.36,
      "text": "either you or your head must be off,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 313.36,
      "end": 315.488,
      "text": "and that in about half no time! Take"
    },
    {
      "start": 315.76,
      "end": 319.44,
      "text": "your choice! The Duchess took her choice, and was"
    },
    {
      "start": 319.44,
      "end": 323.296,
      "text": "gone in a moment. Let's go on with the game, the"
    },
    {
      "start": 323.78,
      "end": 326.06,
      "text": "Queen said to Alice; and Alice was too much"
    },
    {
      "start": 326.06,
      "end": 328.6,
      "text": "frightened to say a word, but slowly followed"
    },
    {
      "start": 328.88,
      "end": 330.22,
      "text": "her back to the croquet-ground."
    },
    {
      "start": 331.56,
      "end": 334.96,
      "text": "The other guests had taken advantage of the Queen's absence, and",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 334.96,
      "end": 336.04,
      "text": "were resting in the shade."
    },
    {
      "start": 336.26,
      "end": 336.36,
      "text": "However,"
    },
    {
      "start": 336.88,
      "end": 337.98,
      "text": "the moment they saw her,"
    },
    {
      "start": 338.1,
      "end": 339.4,
      "text": "they hurried back to the game,"
    },
    {
      "start": 339.76,
      "end": 341.88,
      "text": "the Queen merely remarking that a moment's"
    },
    {
      "start": 341.88,
      "end": 343.34,
      "text": "delay would cost them their lives."
    },
    {
      "start": 344.14,
      "end": 344.8,
      "text": "All the time they",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 344.8,
      "end": 345.26,
      "text": "were playing,"
    },
    {
      "start": 345.4,
      "end": 346.98,
      "text": "the Queen never left off quarrelling"
    },
    {
      "start": 346.98,
      "end": 348.78,
      "text": "with the other players, and shouting,"
    },
    {
      "start": 349.12,
      "end": 349.94,
      "text": "Off with his head!"
    },
    {
      "start": 350.12,
      "end": 352.1,
      "text": "or Off with her head!"
    },
    {
      "start": 353.1,
      "end": 355.6,
      "text": "Those whom she sentenced were taken into custody by",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 355.76,
      "end": 356.08,
      "text": "the soldiers,"
    },
    {
      "start": 356.8,
      "end": 359.64,
      "text": "who of course had to leave off being arches to do this,"
    },
    {
      "start": 359.75,
      "end": 361.38,
      "text": "so that by the end of half an"
    },
    {
      "start": 361.38,
      "end": 363.32,
      "text": "hour or so there were no arches left,"
    },
    {
      "start": 363.46,
      "end": 364.4,
      "text": "and all the players,"
    },
    {
      "start": 364.56,
      "end": 365.42,
      "text": "except the King,"
    },
    {
      "start": 365.54,
      "end": 366.02,
      "text": "the Queen,"
    },
    {
      "start": 366.12,
      "end": 366.56,
      "text": "and Alice,"
    },
    {
      "start": 366.76,
      "end": 369.28,
      "text": "were in custody and under sentence of execution."
    },
    {
      "start": 370.68,
      "end": 371.7,
      "text": "Then the Queen left off,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 371.78,
      "end": 372.54,
      "text": "quite out of breath,"
    },
    {
      "start": 372.76,
      "end": 373.78,
      "text": "and said to Alice,"
    },
    {
      "start": 374.26,
      "end": 375.9,
      "text": "Have you seen the Mock Turtle yet?"
    },
    {
      "start": 376.66,
      "end": 377.24,
      "text": "No,"
    },
    {
      "start": 377.46,
      "end": 378.06,
      "text": "said Alice."
    },
    {
      "start": 378.34,
      "end": 380.0,
      "text": "I don't even know what a Mock Turtle is."
    },
    {
      "start": 382.112,
      "end": 384.6,
      "text": "It's the thing Mock Turtle Soup is made from,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 384.9,
      "end": 385.78,
      "text": "said the Queen."
    },
    {
      "start": 386.36,
      "end": 388.36,
      "text": "I never saw one, or heard of one,"
    },
    {
      "start": 388.46,
      "end": 388.88,
      "text": "said Alice."
    },
    {
      "start": 389.94,
      "end": 390.48,
      "text": "Come on, then,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 390.68,
      "end": 391.44,
      "text": "said the Queen,"
    },
    {
      "start": 391.9,
      "end": 393.18,
      "text": "and he shall tell you his history."
    },
    {
      "start": 394.36,
      "end": 395.38,
      "text": "As they walked off together,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 395.72,
      "end": 399.16,
      "text": "Alice heard the King say in a low voice, to the company generally,"
    },
    {
      "start": 400.448,
      "end": 401.12,
      "text": "You are all pardoned.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 402.22,
      "end": 402.72,
      "text": "Come,"
    },
    {
      "start": 402.76,
      "end": 403.5,
      "text": "_that's_ a good thing!"
    },
    {
      "start": 403.6,
      "end": 404.3,
      "text": "she said to herself,"
    },
    {
      "start": 404.7,
      "end": 406.86,
      "text": "for she had felt quite unhappy at the"
    },
    {
      "start": 406.86,
      "end": 408.72,
      "text": "number of executions the Queen had ordered."
    },
    {
      "start": 410.32,
      "end": 413.7,
      "text": "They very soon came upon a Gryphon, lying fast asleep in the sun.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 414.18,
      "end": 415.54,
      "text": "If you don't know what a Gryphon is,"
    },
    {
      "start": 415.74,
      "end": 416.46,
      "text": "look at the picture."
    },
    {
      "start": 417.42,
      "end": 417.92,
      "text": "Up,"
    },
    {
      "start": 417.98,
      "end": 418.5,
      "text": "lazy thing!"
    },
    {
      "start": 418.89,
      "end": 419.7,
      "text": "said the Queen,"
    },
    {
      "start": 419.9,
      "end": 421.88,
      "text": "and take this young lady to see the Mock Turtle,"
    },
    {
      "start": 422.14,
      "end": 423.32,
      "text": "and to hear his history."
    },
    {
      "start": 424.06,
      "end": 427.2,
      "text": "I must go back and see after some executions I have ordered,"
    },
    {
      "start": 427.76,
      "end": 428.52,
      "text": "and she walked off,"
    },
    {
      "start": 428.56,
      "end": 430.3,
      "text": "leaving Alice alone with the Gryphon."
    },
    {
      "start": 431.072,
      "end": 433.1,
      "text": "Alice did not quite like the look of the creature,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 433.26,
      "end": 435.16,
      "text": "but on the whole she thought it would be quite as"
    },
    {
      "start": 435.16,
      "end": 437.7,
      "text": "safe to stay with it as to go after that savage Queen:"
    },
    {
      "start": 438.36,
      "end": 438.96,
      "text": "so she waited."
    },
    {
      "start": 439.54,
      "end": 441.84,
      "text": "The Gryphon sat up and rubbed its eyes:"
    },
    {
      "start": 442.18,
      "end": 444.44,
      "text": "then it watched the Queen till she was out of sight:"
    },
    {
      "start": 444.9,
      "end": 445.49,
      "text": "then it chuckled."
    },
    {
      "start": 446.26,
      "end": 446.6,
      "text": "What fun!",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 446.86,
      "end": 447.8,
      "text": "said the Gryphon,"
    },
    {
      "start": 447.82,
      "end": 448.48,
      "text": "half to itself,"
    },
    {
      "start": 448.6,
      "end": 449.16,
      "text": "half to Alice."
    },
    {
      "start": 450.5,
      "end": 451.26,
      "text": "What _is_ the fun?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 451.3,
      "end": 451.82,
      "text": "said Alice."
    },
    {
      "start": 452.4,
      "end": 452.5,
      "text": "Why,"
    },
    {
      "start": 452.54,
      "end": 452.66,
      "text": "_she_,"
    },
    {
      "start": 452.88,
      "end": 453.54,
      "text": "said the Gryphon."
    },
    {
      "start": 453.952,
      "end": 454.8,
      "text": "It's all her fancy, that:"
    },
    {
      "start": 455.06,
      "end": 456.14,
      "text": "they never executes nobody,"
    },
    {
      "start": 456.34,
      "end": 456.6,
      "text": "you know."
    },
    {
      "start": 456.7,
      "end": 457.22,
      "text": "Come on!"
    },
    {
      "start": 458.912,
      "end": 460.22,
      "text": "Everybody says 'come on!' here,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 460.34,
      "end": 460.9,
      "text": "thought Alice,"
    },
    {
      "start": 461.06,
      "end": 462.5,
      "text": "as she went slowly after it:"
    },
    {
      "start": 463.02,
      "end": 464.98,
      "text": "I never was so ordered about in my life,"
    },
    {
      "start": 465.22,
      "end": 465.46,
      "text": "never!"
    },
    {
      "start": 466.78,
      "end": 469.04,
      "text": "They had not gone far before they",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 469.04,
      "end": 470.62,
      "text": "saw the Mock Turtle in the distance,"
    },
    {
      "start": 471.0,
      "end": 473.32,
      "text": "sitting sad and lonely on a little ledge of rock,"
    },
    {
      "start": 473.86,
      "end": 475.1,
      "text": "and, as they came nearer,"
    },
    {
      "start": 475.16,
      "end": 477.96,
      "text": "Alice could hear him sighing as if his heart would break."
    },
    {
      "start": 478.56,
      "end": 479.6,
      "text": "She pitied him deeply."
    },
    {
      "start": 480.88,
      "end": 481.66,
      "text": "What is his sorrow?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 481.88,
      "end": 482.9,
      "text": "she asked the Gryphon,"
    },
    {
      "start": 482.98,
      "end": 485.82,
      "text": "and the Gryphon answered, very nearly in the same words as before,"
    },
    {
      "start": 486.528,
      "end": 487.28,
      "text": "It's all his fancy,"
    },
    {
      "start": 487.34,
      "end": 487.54,
      "text": "that:"
    },
    {
      "start": 487.7,
      "end": 488.94,
      "text": "he hasn't got no sorrow,"
    },
    {
      "start": 489.04,
      "end": 489.32,
      "text": "you know."
    },
    {
      "start": 489.44,
      "end": 489.98,
      "text": "Come on!"
    },
    {
      "start": 491.456,
      "end": 492.94,
      "text": "So they went up to the Mock Turtle,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 493.1,
      "end": 495.34,
      "text": "who looked at them with large eyes full of tears,"
    },
    {
      "start": 495.6,
      "end": 496.4,
      "text": "but said nothing."
    }
  ]
}
